{"tid":800780,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實比起老婆係唔係處女 男人更介意老婆係唔係豬扒","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:13:36.000Z","uid":204717,"like":285,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ecbe94f01454d8f0d3df484cf5d142960468c070","tid":800780,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"講真如果有個靚女對你有意思<br />\n理得佢係唔係處你都會心動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢不過係內裡有少少損傷既名牌袋<br />\n就算穿左價值依然一樣係度<br />\n<br />\n相反如果係件豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個處你不過都係一塊無人要既垃圾膠袋等你去篤穿<br />\n五毫子既價值點完整都係得五毫子<br />\n<strong>無需要既時候 可能人地送上門比你都唔會要 毫無價值可言</strong><br />\n<br />\n穿左既名牌袋可以修補 而且外在睇唔到<br />\n但垃圾袋就算點完整都係一個垃圾袋<br />\n你諗下你想對住件名牌袋/拎個名牌袋出街<br />\n定係對住件垃圾袋/拖住件垃圾袋出街?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本有條件既女仔十幾歲破處係好正常<br />\n有件靚女廿幾歲仲係處你都會驚佢有咩問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以連登仔講咩處女唔處女真係好on9<br />\n<br />\n靚女*處女分數大升係事實<br />\n但你底分高過哂底線有哂入場劵既話根本唔需要在意<br />\n<br />\n所以在意條女/自己係唔係處既時候<br />\n不如照下鏡望下自己個樣吸唔吸引到人<br />\n可唔可以令人本能咁對你產生感覺好過啦[<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x] <br />\n<br />\n有條件既女仔一個唔要仲有成村男人排緊隊等住養佢<br />\n係唔係處幾乎毫無影響力可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以講埋咩老婆一定要處女既連登仔十成都係無女人吼既劣等基因柒男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n性愛呢啲緊係十幾歲兩小無猜既時候就趁早享受架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>真係等到廿幾三十歲結婚先同你班幻想中既中坑「成功人士」柒毒男扑野咩</strong><br />\n<strong>水都出唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>同意:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚女A380都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">唔同意:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願要件豬閪處女</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"186457059977b7491d85c583c30fe7832d0248b8","tid":800780,"uid":106468,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"又唔係咁講<br />\n拍過十次拖嘅靚女真係唔係太想同佢做人世埋單<br />\n不過都唔代表要豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad342821b5d87af823ee20ad2ba72e94c0090f3a","tid":800780,"uid":204717,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"已經有不願面對現實既柒毒男偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ed2df692c17171ff651fbe69132bea1deb4828","tid":800780,"uid":53736,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"投你老母閪票咩 係人都睇樣架啦 呃正評 負評唔係因為我要豬閪 係因為你戇鳩"},{"pid":"f2c3a7c3f745a83f033a14b442b4b002b49e3f83","tid":800780,"uid":204717,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"81ed2df692c17171ff651fbe69132bea1deb4828","tid":800780,"uid":53736,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"投你老母閪票咩 係人都睇樣架啦 呃正評 負評唔係因為我要豬閪 係因為你戇鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"正負評6:4喎撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c81f78aadb5cecf6cad137cf955659216de7a9","tid":800780,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"186457059977b7491d85c583